                                <p><b>Cpanel -> Settings -> Doctors</b></p>
                                <p>Fist select the doctor from the "UserDoctorID" dropdown list, then enter the doctors "Medical council number", select "Reservation type" as Selective, and for the "Reservation limitation for days: From" select "With starting visit time" and the "Reservation limitation for days: To" select "With starting visit time". </p>
                                <p>In the description area, input the description of the doctor in all available languages for so it would be shown to the users.</p>
