                            <div class="col-md-12">
                                <h4 id="line8_2">Assign / Remove doctor's specialities / grade</h4>
                                <p><b>1. Assign / Remove doctor's specialities</b></p>
                                <p><b>Cpanel -> Settings -> Doctors -> Specialities</b></p>
                                <p>To assign a speciality to a doctor tap the specialities button <img src="~/images/guide/upload/Specialities_Button.jpg" style="width: 50px; vertical-align: baseline;"> then choose the speciality "Category" and the sub-speciality "Expertise" of the doctor as shown below and then hit <img src="~/images/guide/upload/AddNew.jpg" style="width: 70px; vertical-align: baseline;"> button.</p>
                                <img src="~/images/guide/upload/ChooseSpeciality.jpg" alt="" class="img-responsive img-thumbnail">
                                <p>To remove a speciality to a doctor tap the specialities button <img src="~/images/guide/upload/Specialities_Button.jpg" style="width: 50px; vertical-align: baseline;"> then in the "Doctor expertises list" hit the <img src="~/images/guide/upload/Remove_Button.jpg" style="width: 30px; vertical-align: baseline;"> button.</p>
                                <hr>
                                <p><b>2. Assign / Remove doctor's grades</b></p>
                                <p><b>Cpanel -> Settings -> Doctors -> Grades</b></p>
                                <p>To assign a grade to a doctor tap the grades button <img src="~/images/guide/upload/Grades_Button.jpg" style="width: 30px; vertical-align: baseline;"> then choose the "Grades" and then hit <img src="~/images/guide/upload/Update_Button.jpg" style="width: 50px; vertical-align: baseline;"> button.</p>
                                <p>For removing go to Cpanel -> Settings -> Doctors -> Grades then hit the cross to remove the assigned speciality.</p>
