                                <p>To enable a disabled doctor, first hit on the <img src="~/images/guide/upload/InactiveButton.jpg" style="width: 60px; vertical-align: baseline;"> button then hit <img src="~/images/guide/upload/Enabling_Button.jpg" style="width: 60px; vertical-align: baseline;"> button.</p>

