                                <img src="~/images/guide/upload/VisitInfoWindow.jpg" alt="" class="img-responsive img-thumbnail">
                                <p>3. In the treatment section <img src="~/images/guide/upload/Treatements_Button.jpg" style="width: 80px; vertical-align: sub;"> tap <img src="~/images/guide/upload/NewPlusButton.jpg" style="width: 60px; vertical-align: sub;"> .</p>
