                                <p>In the treatments section as shown below, you have the list of treatments for the patient in the "Drug" drop down. If the drug you searched is not available in the "Drug" drop down, write it in the "Drug Name" field.</p>
                                <img src="~/images/guide/upload/Treatements_Section.jpg" alt="" class="img-responsive img-thumbnail">
